{"tid":995483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏薩特回應沙利：我無所謂 你鐘意講乜就乜","createTime":"2019-01-25T12:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T13:19:55.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2272b40e77e6585367b8b1a8fa4fba03396c2828","tid":995483,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"　　車路士教練沙利日前點評夏薩特「不是領袖」，這也引起了軒然大波。在車路士戰勝熱刺挺進聯賽盃決賽後，夏薩特也做出了回應。<br />\n<br />\n　　此前沙利點評夏薩特時稱：「 他必須先尊重自己，他必須做更多。現在，夏薩特更像一個獨立的球員，而不是一個領袖。他是個偉大的球員，他總能夠在2分鐘內贏波，有時甚至只需要1分鐘。但是現在，他不是一個領袖。他是一名好球員，也許是世界最佳之一。」<br />\n<br />\n　　而在戰神熱刺後，夏薩特對沙利的這番言論做出了回應。夏薩特稱：「無所謂。我不在乎這些。我只會踢我自己的足球。教練說了什麼都沒什麼影響。我只會專注於我自己的足球，只會想著把我最好的狀態奉獻給全隊。」"},{"pid":"b29cd919c43fbc6b4c2276d3e42a7f388139f262","tid":995483,"uid":21275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d872aa2c311efe91751b2af2ef6fbe9d549c6f7","tid":995483,"uid":186145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"去皇馬啦"},{"pid":"d588d3766b759af3ffd0bc23ec9223e693cc7925","tid":995483,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"戰神熱刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a379057d67840868f4907a887f2f8c160b927aec","tid":995483,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d588d3766b759af3ffd0bc23ec9223e693cc7925","tid":995483,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"戰神熱刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"唔小心講咗事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3b224c18cee78bddd3c142f59cebbdd842859b","tid":995483,"uid":8951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d588d3766b759af3ffd0bc23ec9223e693cc7925","tid":995483,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12: